{"data":[{"date":"15:52 20/08","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP U23 Malaysia vs U23 Bahrain 19h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/u23-malaysia-vs-u23-bahrain-tran-dau-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp U23 Malaysia vs U23 Bahrain: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Olympic Malaysia vs Olympic Bahrain b\u1ea3ng E Asiad 2018 l\u00fac 19h00 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 20/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">(\u1ea5n Ctrl + F5 \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t)<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Malaysia th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018. Sau khi ki\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Kyrgyzstan \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n khi h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Asiad, \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho t\u1ea5m HCV \u1edf k\u1ef3 n\u0103m nay, U23 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 2-1. U23 Malaysia th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc 2 b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p 1 v\u00e0 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 1 b\u00e0n thua trong kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHai th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00fap U23 Malaysia s\u1edbm gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00f2ng 1/8, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1edf h\u1eefu lu\u00f4n ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Bahrain ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n mang \u00fd ngh\u0129a th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c v\u00e0 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ong Kim g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd d\u01b0\u1ee1ng s\u1ee9c cho v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Bahrain gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i U23 Malaysia b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 n\u00e0o. Khi \u0111\u00f3, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 ch\u1ec9 x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c song v\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong tay th\u00ec U23 Bahrain ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 d\u01b0\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch 1/4 \u0111\u1ed9i x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 3 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Do ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1eafng l\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam U23 Malaysia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u00fat \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c n\u00e0o th\u00ec tin r\u1eb1ng U23 Bahrain s\u1ebd ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2579","checkdouble":"194908"},{"date":"16:28 20/08","title":"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/3/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Andrew Robertson \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAndrew Robertson chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool t\u1eeb Hull City \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2017 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 8 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Scotland \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/9/Liverpool-muon-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-Andrew-Robertson-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Andrew Robertson \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Robertson \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Moreno \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 4 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Champions League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGiai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y Robertson c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 b\u00ean h\u00e0nh lang c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong c\u1ea3 vai tr\u00f2 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/andrew-robertson-mon-hoi-cua-liverpool-172-183666.html\" target=\"_blank\">Robertson l\u00e0 m\u00f3n h\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ngu\u1ed3n tin cho r\u1eb1ng PSG v\u00e0 Real quan t\u00e2m Robertson, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Kop nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Andrew Robertson, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u00ean \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Robertson v\u1edbi Liverpool c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2021, song Liverpool mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n th\u00eam 2 n\u0103m v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Scotland.\u00a0Hi\u1ec7n m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 anh \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 25.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, \u1edf b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi Robertson s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103ng l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00ean 60.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng mu\u1ed1n gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Robertson trong th\u00e1ng 8 n\u00e0y. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng The Kop thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Anfield v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c c\u00f9ng HLV Klopp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i West Ham 4-0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. \u0110\u00eam nay, The Kop s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Crystal Palace \u1edf v\u00f2ng 2, m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2578","checkdouble":"194909"},{"date":"16:10 20/08","title":"B\u00e1c s\u0129 c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/bac-si-cua-olympic-viet-nam-ly-giai-nguyen-nhan-xuan-truong-ngoi-du-bi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn anh v\u1edbi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Barca bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Firmino l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i \u0111ang mang tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn lao t\u1eeb NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPremier League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cay \u0111\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho The Kop trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hoi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-2h-ngay-218-khang-dinh-suc-manh-172-194876.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crystal Palace vs Liverpool (2h ng\u00e0y 21/8): Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2577","checkdouble":"194910"},{"date":"16:50 20/08","title":"Arsenal nh\u1eadn tin c\u1ef1c bu\u1ed3n t\u1eeb Aaron Ramsey","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Ramsey \u0111ang b\u1ebf t\u1eafc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Arsenal \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ramsey. H\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2019, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ramsey.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/arsenal-nhan-tin-cuc-buon-tu-aaron-ramsey.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal ch\u01b0a gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n gia h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Ramsey, song m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, kh\u00fac m\u1eafc \u1edf m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Ramsey k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u00e0 Ramsey \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf Arsenal l\u00e0 110.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00f2i 300.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 250.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n m\u1edbi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Arsenal ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng gi\u1eefa hai b\u00ean ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 12 th\u00e1ng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Ramsey \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u00e0 Chelsea quan t\u00e2m Ramsey</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, Aaron Ramsey r\u1eddi Arsenal \u1edf H\u00e8 2019 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Tuong-lai-Ramsey-o-Arsenal-duoc-phong-len-hang-huyen-thoai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn quan t\u00e2m Aaron Ramsey</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u0103m t\u1edbi, Ramsey c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111ang l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng vi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y s\u1ee9c \u00e9p bu\u1ed9c Arsenal ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-muon-mua-ramsey-va-vecino-172-192315.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Ramsey</span>, hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i. 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2019.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t tr\u1eafng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 28 tu\u1ed5i. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Ramsey r\u1ea5t gi\u1ed1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec x\u1ea3y ra v\u1edbi Mesut Ozil v\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Ramsey \u1edf l\u1ea1i, Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m v\u1edbi Ozil. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e0 Ramsey \u0111\u00f2i h\u1ecfi, Arsenal s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ho\u1eb7c thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Sanchez.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2576","checkdouble":"194911"},{"date":"16:50 20/08","title":"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/3-cau-thu-mu-xung-dang-bi-tram-khoi-doi-hinh-chinh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. HLV Jose Mourinho th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng thay \u0111\u1ed5i trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a MU l\u00fac n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Juan Mata\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3m kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb tr\u1ea3m kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/164704-1.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juan Mata kh\u00f4ng mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o cho h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. \u0110\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0ng Mata r\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1eddi tham gia ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i c\u1ee7a anh khi\u1ebfn Young kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng tr\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Brighton c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1. Mata kh\u00f4ng k\u00e8m c\u1eb7p h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Brighton v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea9y Young kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. Khi \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Solly March \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 tung c\u00fa t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cho Murray m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, Mata c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 m\u1ea5t t\u00edch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n khi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng v\u00ec m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y m\u00e0 Mata \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Mourinho thay ra ngay sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9 gi\u1eefa hi\u1ec7p. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Mata trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Eric Bailly\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bailly Lindelof\" title=\"Bailly Lindelof\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bailly ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i ng\u1edb ng\u1ea9n khi\u1ebfn MU nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Eric Bailly \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o MU. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Bailly r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t khao ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh n\u0103m nay. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1edd Bi\u1ec3n Ng\u00e0 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ea9n khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Brighton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBailly l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi\u1ebfn Man United ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu qu\u1ea3 penalty \u1edf ph\u00fat 43, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eeba c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 1-2. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o kh\u1ecfi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i s\u1eeda sai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBailly c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n v\u1eeba qua c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao cho Jones ho\u1eb7c Smalling, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Anthony Martial\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anthony Martial\" title=\"Anthony Martial\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/164715-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Anthony Martial m\u1ea5t \u0111i kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng khoan ph\u00e1 th\u1ea7n th\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial ch\u01a1i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i trong vi\u1ec7c c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y kh\u00f3 t\u00ednh Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMartial \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch xuy\u00ean th\u1ee7ng h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Brighton. Anh c\u0169ng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng t\u00ecm \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Lukaku trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Brighton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede kh\u00eda c\u1ea1nh ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, Martial t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t k\u00e9m v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3m t\u1ea3i \u00e1p l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Luke Shaw b\u00ean c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng b\u1ecb Mourinho thay ra trong hi\u1ec7p hai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u00ecn chung, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Martial m\u00f9a n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd g\u1eafn ch\u1eb7t tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn \u0111ang d\u1ed3n n\u00e9n v\u1edbi Mourinho, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd Martial s\u1ebd t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ra \u0111i trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brighton-32-mu-172-194892.html\">2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/4-cau-thu-choi-te-nhat-cua-mu-truoc-brighton-172-194886.html\">4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a MU tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2575","checkdouble":"194913"},{"date":"17:04 20/08","title":"Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf l\u1ea1i Liverpool l\u00e2u d\u00e0i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n g\u1eafn anh v\u1edbi Barcelona trong th\u1eddi gian qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb T\u00e2y Ban Nha, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1edbi Liverpool h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 4. B\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Barca bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eaft t\u1edbi nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n Firmino l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u1edf Liverpool v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield l\u00e2u d\u00e0i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Firmino n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc tin \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/firmino-noi-gi-truoc-tin-don-dau-quan-cho-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Firmino cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nghe c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn khi b\u1ea1n th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i qua c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3 th\u00ec b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTrong c\u1ea3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi t\u00f4i, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ed1t nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd. T\u00f4i \u0111ang mang tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p l\u1ea1i ni\u1ec1m tin l\u1edbn lao t\u1eeb NHM.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPremier League v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ch\u00ednh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb thu h\u00fat sau khi l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League v\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn thua \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng cay \u0111\u1eafng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfn t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh t\u1ef1u nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nFirmino kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung t\u1ed1i \u0111a v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1edf Liverpool hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111em l\u1ea1i th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho The Kop trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cKhi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hoi t\u00f4i v\u1ec1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau trong ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p th\u00ec t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1ng cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn xa h\u01a1n th\u1ebf m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp theo.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 C\u0110V nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. H\u1ecd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. V\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 cho h\u1ecd\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-2h-ngay-218-khang-dinh-suc-manh-172-194876.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Crystal Palace vs Liverpool (2h ng\u00e0y 21/8): Kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2574","checkdouble":"194914"},{"date":"17:18 20/08","title":"V\u00ec Chelsea, HLV Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea sau 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Premier League. Chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 \u0111ang d\u1ef1 t\u00ednh ng\u1eebng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3 to\u00e0n t\u00e2m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea to\u00e0n th\u1eafng 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Chelsea ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n. Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Antonio Conte b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Sau tr\u1eadn thua Man City t\u1ea1i Community Shield, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Sarri \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 59 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9nh \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i The Blues kh\u1edfi s\u1eafc tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i Premier League 2018/19, Chelsea \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p Huddersfield Town 3-0 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch. Ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Arsenal 3-2 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Stamford Bridge. T\u00ednh t\u1edbi l\u00fac n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Sarri t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean BXH, c\u00f9ng c\u00f3 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng k\u00e9m h\u01a1n Man City hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u2013 b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/hlv-maurizio-sarri-phat-bieu-ve-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2>Sarri nguy\u1ec7n b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea, quy \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng h\u00fat thu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng Anh khi\u1ebfn cho Maurizio Sarri g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u nh\u1eb1m t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ef1 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, Maurizio Sarri ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Chelsea l\u1ea1i cho th\u1ea5y quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m l\u1edbn b\u1ecf thu\u1ed1c l\u00e1. \u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea7n gi\u1edd gi\u1ea3i lao v\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ebfu thu\u1ed1c\u201d, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean. \u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i 1 ho\u1eb7c 2 n\u0103m sau \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u00fat tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi Arsenal, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u00e9p s\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 pressing, kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 g\u1eb7p r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i. Trong hi\u1ec7p 2, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh. R\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i hi\u1ec7p 1. T\u00f4i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea-172-194881.html\">Morata: T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-mot-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal-du-suc-dung-trong-doi-hinh-chelsea-172-194868.html\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-kovacic-noi-gi-sau-man-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194861.html\">T\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-chia-se-ly-do-hut-chet-truoc-arsenal-172-194835.html\">Sao Chelsea chia s\u1ebb l\u00fd do h\u00fat ch\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hazard-chinh-thuc-co-cau-tra-loi-cho-real-madrid-172-194831.html\">Hazard ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi cho Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2573","checkdouble":"194915"},{"date":"17:15 20/08","title":"Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/berbatov-len-tieng-tran-an-cdv-mu-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Dimitar Berbatov cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c C\u0110V MU kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Brighton ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m qua. Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Mourinho cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m l\u1edbn l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n ch\u00ednh d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Amex. Nh\u01b0ng Berbatov kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00e2y gi\u1edd m\u1edbi l\u00e0 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00e0 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i lo l\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Berbatov tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Berbatov tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V MU sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/berbatov-len-tieng-tran-an-cdv-mu-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Berbatov l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an C\u0110V\u00a0MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t video \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang Instagram, Berbatov cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edd t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i. Nh\u01b0ng coi n\u00e0o, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm. \u0110\u1eebng qu\u00e1 lo l\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n th\u1eafng, \u0111\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n thua. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 b\u1ea1n lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n. V\u1eady n\u00ean h\u00e3y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, Man United s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Tottenham v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 27/8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 Burnley v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 2/9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMourinho ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u1ed9t chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Antonio Valencia v\u00e0 Nemanja Matic \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n ng\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00e1c v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 nh\u1eb9. D\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Spurs v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-cau-thu-mu-xung-dang-bi-tram-khoi-doi-hinh-chinh-172-194913.html\">3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng b\u1ecb \u201ctr\u1ea3m\u201d kh\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/2-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-brighton-32-mu-172-194892.html\">2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Brighton 3-2 MU</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2572","checkdouble":"194916"},{"date":"17:53 20/08","title":"L\u00fd do Liverpool s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c cho Alisson?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/ly-do-liverpool-su-dung-tui-bong-bau-duc-cho-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a HLV Jurgen Klopp, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p gi\u00fap cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd th\u00edch nghi v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng Premier League.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Alisson t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 65 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u01b0\u1ee3t qua m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eebng s\u1ecf t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Chelsea, The Kop \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Brazil.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n Liverpool b\u1ecf ra \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Alisson t\u1eebng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb Chelsea v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Kepa Arrizabalaga. C\u00e1ch m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u00f9ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t l\u1ea1 m\u1eaft. <br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/ly-do-liverpool-su-dung-tui-bong-bau-duc-cho-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, Alisson d\u00f9ng t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Liverpool. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 John Achterberg \u0111\u01b0a ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Klopp l\u00fd gi\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong l\u00fac m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f2n \u0111ang b\u00e1n t\u00edn b\u00e1n nghi v\u1ec1 l\u00fd do \u0111\u1eb1ng sau vi\u1ec7c t\u00fai b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Liverpool, HLV Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch. \u201c\u0110\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng b\u1ea7u d\u1ee5c, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 b\u00e0i t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n\u201d, chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch v\u1edbi c\u00e1c ph\u00f3ng vi\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi Loris Karius gia nh\u1eadp, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. D\u0129 nhi\u00ean, kh\u00f4ng l\u00fd g\u00ec Alisson kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng khi hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n. Vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a b\u1edfi v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i khu v\u1ef1c an to\u00e0n d\u00e0nh cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, c\u00f3 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 15 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t. Kh\u00f4ng h\u1eb3n m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00ec Premier League. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Alisson. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ecbu tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Ngo\u00e0i Alisson, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f2n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/truoc-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tiep-tuc-bung-no-chu-sadio-mane-172-194919.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace vs Liverpool: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9 Sadio Mane?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/robertson-sap-duoc-liverpool-thuong-lon-172-194909.html\">Andrew Robertson s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Liverpool th\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/dortmund-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-origi-172-194891.html\">Dortmund s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-palace-lo-ngai-ve-su-nguy-hiem-cua-salah-172-194870.html\">HLV Palace lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Liverpool?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-canh-bao-cac-hoc-tro-ve-cho-dung-bap-benh-o-liverpool-172-194860.html\">Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u1ec1 ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u1ea5p b\u00eanh \u1edf Liverpool</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2571","checkdouble":"194917"},{"date":"17:44 20/08","title":"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Crystal Palace vs Liverpool: Ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9 Sadio Mane?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/20/truoc-tran-crystal-palace-vs-liverpool-tiep-tuc-bung-no-chu-sadio-mane.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, The Kop v\u00f9i d\u1eadp West Ham tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0. L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u1ee7ng khi\u1ebfp, Sadio Mane l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt ch\u00ednh trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Crystal Palace vs Liverpool Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Crystal Palace vs Liverpool Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Crystal-Palace-vs-Liverpool-Sadio-Mane-toa-sang-ruc-ro-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i. Sadio Mane ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal li\u00ean t\u1ee5c khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 West Ham trao \u0111\u1ea3o b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Ryan Fredericks \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 khi ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i b\u00ean ph\u00eda Liverpool, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Mane \u0111\u00e3 3 l\u1ea7n v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a West Ham. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 l\u00e0 m\u1ed1i \u0111e d\u1ecda th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1ef1c v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch v\u1edbi 4 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSalah v\u00e0 Mane l\u00e0 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n (4 l\u1ea7n), song ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. Salah d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 4 l\u1ea7n, tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch 3 nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i Mane ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang khung th\u00e0nh nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMane l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-0 cho Liverpool sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a James Milner, sau \u0111\u00f3 anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t nhanh v\u00e0 hi\u1ec3m sau \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a Roberto Firmino.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a Liverpool t\u1ea1i Premier League. Sadio Mane \u0111\u00e3 tham gia tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0o 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Liverpool sau 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u West Ham t\u1ea1i Premier League (3 b\u00e0n, 3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ban do nhiet cua Mane o tran dau voi West Ham\" title=\"B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Mane \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mane-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed3 nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a Mane \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi West Ham, Mane c\u00f2n t\u1ea1o ra 2 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 3 l\u1ea7n t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng. C\u1ef1u sao Southampton di chuy\u1ec3n tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp m\u1eb7t s\u00e2n v\u00e0 tham gia v\u00e0o m\u1ecdi ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng, t\u1eeb h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Mane \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u m\u1ec7t m\u1ecfi, anh v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t sung m\u00e3n v\u00e0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 Salah ch\u01b0a l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f2n Roberto Firmino ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng, Mane l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u0169i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mane s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sadio Mane t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 c\u1ee7a Liverpool tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do \u0111\u1ec3 tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Crystal Palace trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 2 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mane luon rat co duyen voi manh luoi Crystal Palace\" title=\"Mane lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/mane.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mane lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 duy\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi West Ham, Mane \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Senegal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i mang v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi con m\u1ed3i quen thu\u1ed9c mang t\u00ean Crystal Palace.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 26 tu\u1ed5i lu\u00f4n r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 duy\u00ean trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Crystal Palalce. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, trong 7 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Selhurst Park ch\u00e2n s\u00fat sinh n\u0103m 1992 ghi t\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Trong s\u1ed1 20 \u0111\u1ed9i tham d\u1ef1 Premier League 2018/19, Palace l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00e0 Mane s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Mane ghi b\u00e0n trong c\u1ea3 hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Palace \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. \u1ede tr\u1eadn l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Anfield anh ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng duy nh\u1ea5t gi\u00fap L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0111\u1ecf gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 1-0, t\u1ea1i Selhurst Park c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i ghi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1edf ra c\u00fa l\u1ed9i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Liverpool (th\u1eafng 2-1).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao sau 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi West Ham c\u00f9ng c\u00e1i duy\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0nh l\u01b0\u1edbi Crystal Palace l\u00e0 ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 Liverpool h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, qua \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u1edbi Man City, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t Huddersfield 6-1 \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2570","checkdouble":"194919"},{"date":"09:46 20/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8 (ASIAD 2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/nhan-dinh-u23-trieu-tien-vs-u23-saudi-arabia-16h00-ngay-208-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia l\u00fac 16h00 ng\u00e0y 20/8(V\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asian 2018): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia 16h00 ng\u00e0y 208 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/U23_Saudi_Arabia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span>U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean vs U23 Saudi Arabia: 1-2<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nU23 Saudi Arabia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 c\u00e1nh c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. Ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 U23 Saudi Arabia v\u00e0o v\u00f2n 1/8, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y mong mu\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n th\u1ebf.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nU23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean h\u00f2a U23 Myanmar \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5 g\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a U23 Iran (thua 0-3) \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 2 n\u00ean \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00e1ch quan, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ki\u1ebfm v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng sau c\u1ee7a U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n n\u1eb1m tr\u00ean l\u00fd thuy\u1ebft d\u00f9 r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 s\u1ebd l\u1ea1i r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf song U23 Saudi Arabia r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng tr\u1ed9i h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChuy\u00ean gia \u0111ang c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng quay l\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean. T\u00ednh t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng 1 cho t\u1edbi nay, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 8 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. V\u1edbi th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea n\u00e0y vi\u1ec7c g\u1eedi g\u1eafm hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o U23 Tri\u1ec1u Ti\u00ean th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bang F ASIAD\" title=\"B\u1ea3ng F ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/19/BXH-bang-F-truoc-luot-dau-cuoi.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2569","checkdouble":"194877"},{"date":"10:31 20/08","title":"Anthony Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, Big Sam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Martial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Big Sam ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Big Sam ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/anthony-martial-bi-chi-trich-du-doi-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 1 g\u1eb7p Leicester, Martial \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer c\u1ee7a Brighton, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mourinho-noi-gi-ve-chan-thuong-cua-alexis-sanchez-172-194874.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sanchez ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span> bu\u1ed9c Mourinho ph\u1ea3i trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Martial.\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ef1u sao Monaco ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMartial ch\u01a1i m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, d\u00f9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 4-3-3, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t\u00a0\u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch n\u00e0o, anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n, Martial ch\u1ec9 tung ra duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf ph\u00fat 59, sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Mourinho kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch Martial</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anthony Martial g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 b\u1ecb c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh Sam Allardyce ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u1eef d\u1ed9i sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, Big Sam kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Falmer.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial bi chi trich sau tran thua Brighton\" title=\"Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/martial-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Martial b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch sau tr\u1eadn thua Brighton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Brighton, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Martial l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a M.U \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Brighton, ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y khi\u1ebfn M.U ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMartial t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng l\u1edbn, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Sterling v\u00e0 Sane. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 k\u00e9m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ee7a Man City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 M.U b\u1ecf ra\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao M.U l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Martial \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, s\u1ebd h\u1ee3p l\u00fd h\u01a1n n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i v\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 kh\u00e1c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2568","checkdouble":"194878"},{"date":"10:11 20/08","title":"Scholes \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/scholes-chi-trich-pogba-sau-tran-thua-brighton.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. C\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y tin r\u1eb1ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00e3 thi\u1ebfu \u0111i s\u1ef1 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho trong c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>M.U tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1 v\u00ec chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Man United ch\u1ec9 mang v\u1ec1 3 t\u00e2n binh bao g\u1ed3m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Fred, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Lee Grant. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ec9 1 trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Fred v\u1eeba \u00fd HLV Jose Mourinho. Nh\u1eefng Dalot non kinh nghi\u1ec7m hay Grant l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p t\u1ee9c th\u00ec.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c M.U li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a Tottenham v\u00e0 Harry Maguire c\u1ee7a Leicester City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ebfn cu\u1ed1i phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 2018 d\u00e0nh cho c\u00e1c CLB Premier League, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU v\u00e0 Mourinho h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/Gary-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-MU-va-Mourinho-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">M.U \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ec7 qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 M.U c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n k\u00e9m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf. T\u1ea1i Premier League, sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, h\u1ecd th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 2-3 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Brighton \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Neville ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o M.U</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U. Anh tin r\u1eb1ng Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Ed Woodward c\u00f9ng l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ea7n h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Mourinho trong mua s\u1eafm n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n b\u00f9 \u0111\u1eafp cho nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sau khi Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2013.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho\" title=\"HLV Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/gary-neville-phat-bieu-ve-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U v\u00e0 Mourinho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho \u0111ang \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 3 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\u201d, Neville n\u00f3i tr\u00ean Sky Sports. \u201cB\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi 3/4 l\u00e0 \u0111ang x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3 v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh vi\u1ec7c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Sau \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n ho\u1eb7c cho thu\u00ea n\u00f3.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKh\u00f4ng ai nh\u1eadn ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 n\u1ebfu n\u00f3 c\u00f2n dang d\u1edf. M.U \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Sir Alex Ferguson ngh\u1ec9 h\u01b0u. Nh\u1eefng David Moyes v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Louis van Gaal \u0111\u00e3 chi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 700 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMourinho c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 th\u00eam. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 CLB n\u00ean h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y. B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u1ee7y b\u1ecf m\u1ed9t d\u1ef1 \u00e1n khi c\u00f2n \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng. Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u trong t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n nay.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng M.U tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zizou-da-san-sang-thay-jose-mourinho-o-mu-172-194539.html\">Zizou \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng thay Jose Mourinho \u1edf M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-cua-minh-172-194297.html\">T\u1ea1i sao Pogba ch\u01b0a c\u00f4ng khai mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-chuyen-nhuong-that-bai-den-nguoi-nha-con-bo-mac-mourinho-172-194167.html\">M.U chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ea5t b\u00e1t: \u0110\u1ebfn \u201cng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00e0\u201d c\u00f2n b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Mourinho!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2567","checkdouble":"194879"},{"date":"10:52 20/08","title":"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/6/real-madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-cavani-len-63-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf, song g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chi 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Real Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/6/Chi-63-trieu-bang,-Real-Madrid-quyet-tam-mua-Edinson-Cavani-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNeymar, Mbappe v\u00e0 Hazard l\u00e0 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, song nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 si\u00eau kh\u1ee7ng cho Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe th\u00ec Hazard l\u1ea1i cam k\u1ebft g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Chelsea.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Karim Benzema, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi Edinson Cavani c\u1ee7a PSG. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, PSG \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-phap/hlv-psg-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-edinson-cavani-197-192355.html\" target=\"_blank\">HLV Thomas Tuchel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Cavani</span>, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ph\u00eda PSG t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn, song Real Madrid v\u1eabn nu\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a TBN v\u1eeba c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Real Madrid n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua sao kh\u1ee7ng PSG l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/18/Real-Madrid-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-khung-PSG-len-63-trieu-bang-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Edinson Cavani l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nReal Madrid quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m mua Edinson Cavani, theo Diario Gol \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay l\u00ean 63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui tin r\u1eb1ng Cavani s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Benzema, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u0103n b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Napoli.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n63 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, nh\u01b0ng PSG s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n Cavani cho Real n\u1ebfu t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Cavani, nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd nh\u01b0 Morata hay Lewandowski \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. N\u1ebfu PSG kh\u00f4ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat t\u1ed1t, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd s\u1ebd t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Cavani cho Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2566","checkdouble":"194880"},{"date":"10:26 20/08","title":"Morata: \"T\u00f4i ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n r\u1eddi Chelsea\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c r\u1eddi Chelsea v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Morata m\u1edbi ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League trong n\u0103m 2018. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a anh b\u1ecb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng d\u1ea5y l\u00ean. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u1edf Serie A c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 La Liga \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Morata trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng ng\u00f4i sao 25 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n HLV Sarri. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 b\u00e0n trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a The Blues tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Arsenal h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Morata ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tin \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/20/morata-toi-chua-tung-nghi-den-chuyen-roi-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Morata ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn tin \u0111\u1ed3n mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Morata quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m x\u00f3a h\u1ebft nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u1edf Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ra \u0111i. V\u1edbi t\u00f4i, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u1eb7c Italia. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi tin t\u01b0\u1edfng </em><em>v\u00e0o t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng k\u1ebb th\u00f9 gh\u00e9t t\u00f4i m\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng cho ch\u00ednh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang t\u00ednh chuy\u1ec7n mua nh\u00e0 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ee9a b\u00e9 l\u1edbn l\u00ean v\u00e0 \u0111i h\u1ecdc \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. T\u1ea1i sao t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac ch\u1ee9. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i suy ngh\u0129 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do t\u00f4i \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu Chelsea n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00ec t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00f3n b\u00f3ng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn v\u00e0 l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u1eddng. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Gi\u1edd thi t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o c\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ea1m v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e9n nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3n c\u00e1c qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t. M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u v\u1edbi t\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/khong-mot-cau-thu-nao-cua-arsenal-du-suc-dung-trong-doi-hinh-chelsea-172-194868.html\">Kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ee9ng trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-binh-kovacic-noi-gi-sau-man-ra-mat-chelsea-172-194861.html\">T\u00e2n binh Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2565","checkdouble":"194881"}]}